OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cafter 'extremely' high patient numbers
OL,6,FSouthmead Hospital in Bristol has
OL,7,Fdeclared a critical incident because
OL,8,Fof "extremely high patient numbers."
OL,10,FPatients are being urged to only
OL,11,Fattend A&E if they require critical
OL,12,Fcare, as they may have to wait more
OL,13,Fthan eight hours to be seen.
OL,15,FThe hospital declared the critical
OL,16,Fincident on 3 December, and issued a
OL,17,Fstatement alerting patients. It reads:
OL,18,F"We have today declared a Critical
OL,19,FIncident at Southmead Hospital due to
OL,20,Fextremely high patient numbers across
OL,21,Fall areas of our hospital.
