OL,6,F"Please do not attend our Emergency
OL,7,FDepartment unless you require
OL,8,Fcritical, lifesaving care.
OL,10,F"If you attend our Emergency
OL,11,FDepartment with a non-life-threatening
OL,12,Fcondition, you may wait more than
OL,13,Feight hours to be seen and/or be sent
OL,14,Fto a more appropriate service
OL,15,Felsewhere.
OL,17,F"Please consider using alternative
OL,18,Fservices, such as your local pharmacy
OL,19,For NHS 111.
